[metadata]
Name:Sengir Vampire Gets +1/+1 When Damaged Creature Dies
Goal:Win
Turns:5
Difficulty:Medium
Description:Sengir Vampire (4/4 Flying) attacks a 1/1 Grizzly Bears variant (here using Birds of Paradise, a 0/1 with flying so it can block flying). When the blocked creature dies from Sengir's combat damage, a +1/+1 counter is placed on Sengir.

Setup uses Grizzly Bears (2/2) as blocker so Sengir kills Grizzly with overflow damage; Sengir survives (4 vs 2). After combat, Sengir should have a +1/+1 counter and be 5/5.

